Document: EngineDebugger
Path: godot/classes/class_enginedebugger.rst
Summary: Describes the EngineDebugger class, which handles communication between the editor and the running game, and manages profilers.

EngineDebugger handles the communication between the editor and the running game. It is active in the running game. Messages can be sent/received through it. It also manages the profilers.
